channel.title: RS543 Deob
channel.description:
It's setup for IntelliJ, but it's a RS543 Deob, which you can compile and run. It's untouched, other than fixing the compile errors and adding a loader + frame.
[b]Mirrors:[/b] [url=http://rsbot2.com/~elohel/rs543.rar]http://rsbot2.com/~elohel/rs543.rar[/url] Thanks to The_Flames and ByteMe, for providing mirrors.
[b]Changelog:[/b] [url=http://naziworld.com/aelin/deobs/RS543.txt]http://naziworld.com/aelin/deobs/RS543.txt[/url]
Parts of the Applet stub are taken from RSBot, so it's GPL code.
I'll be uploading all future deobs to: [url=http://naziworld.com/aelin/deobs/]http://naziworld.com/aelin/deobs/[/url]
